data.description: Experience comfort & style in this exquisite 4 bed, 2.5 bath home in Tehaleh. The spacious living room seamlessly connects to a large kitchen with SS appliances & ample storage, providing an ideal space for gatherings. The primary bedroom, with an elegant ensuite, is a private retreat, and 2 additional bedrooms offer walk-in closets for convenience. Ascend the staircase to an open loft area, perfect for a home office or entertainment space. Enjoy central air conditioning as you explore the thoughtful design. Step into the private backyard oasis for relaxation. Explore 30+ miles of trails, parks, and the community center to enhance your vibrant lifestyle. This home seamlessly blends luxury with nature, inviting you to make Tehaleh your home.
